(defmethod load-begin ((this level))
  "MVP port 2026-05-05 from jak3 (engine/level/level.gc:1000-1755).
   Skips PS2 page-allocation and borrow-slot logic; carves the full
   *level*.heap region for this single loading level (jakx's level
   heap is sized ~12MB which fits one level worth of streamed data).
   Reaches the actual dgo-load-begin RPC call so the IOP-side load
   path can fire and load-continue can advance the state machine."
